503cb41ce397dc77b91cf834666da4feed32cb1f0daa158fbd29a70c234787e7aa8592fb2608de53c614fb8e42a12ced4e7133d3c854d5ff291a06df9ff1ba40  0001-kasts-Fix-dialog-boxes-after-recent-Kirigami-updates.patch
"
